Parse content lines in linear time. The unfolding and whitespace-stripping regexes in :mod:`icalendar.parser.content_line` re-tried a greedy run at every position, so a small calendar carrying a long run of bare line breaks or of spaces around a parameter delimiter made :meth:`Component.from_ical <icalendar.cal.component.Component.from_ical>` take seconds. The patched regexes match the same strings without the quadratic blow-up. @alhudz
